It's how we took an action game like Borderlands

76
00:03:35,823 --> 00:03:36,964
and turned it into an adventure game.

77
00:03:36,984 --> 00:03:40,366
And it's how we're taking 20 seasons of content

78
00:03:40,787 --> 00:03:44,089
and developing them into an RPG that feels like South Park.

79
00:03:46,605 --> 00:03:52,851
In summary, this is really just how do I make this game, level, mission, combat, etc. feel like blah.

80
00:03:52,931 --> 00:03:59,657
