00:07:07,619 --> 00:07:10,681
It's not done being built, but there's still these opulent boardrooms.

139
00:07:10,821 --> 00:07:11,941
There's a roof and a helipad.

140
00:07:11,961 --> 00:07:17,184
And the important thing about our ware here is the details, of course,

