00:07:17,284 --> 00:07:20,206
but also the feelings that...

142
00:07:21,827 --> 00:07:23,028
those spaces create.

143
00:07:23,108 --> 00:07:24,689
So there's a lot of verticality,

144
00:07:24,829 --> 00:07:27,392
it creates feelings of vertigo, of claustrophobia.

145
00:07:27,692 --> 00:07:29,133
They make McLean feel very isolated

