00:08:19,231 --> 00:08:20,891
There's also parallel storytelling.

164
00:08:20,931 --> 00:08:22,932
And what I mean by that is we're cutting

165
00:08:22,992 --> 00:08:24,432
between those characters.

166
00:08:25,132 --> 00:08:27,373
We're looking at a little bit of what McLean's doing

167
00:08:27,433 --> 00:08:29,113
versus what a little bit of the terrorists are doing.

168
00:08:30,213 --> 00:08:32,474
And then those moments,

169
00:08:33,734 --> 00:08:35,334
we're seeing slow, suspenseful moments.

170
00:08:35,994 --> 00:08:38,675
And they quickly ramp into and back out of action.

171
00:08:38,775 --> 00:08:41,575
So you can see kind of this cadence of those events

172
00:08:41,615 --> 00:08:44,236
that happen in those linear and parallel storylines.

173
00:08:45,708 --> 00:08:47,149
And then the How, which is a big one.

174
00:08:47,169 --> 00:08:49,472
Lots of suspense, it's a thriller.

175
00:08:50,753 --> 00:08:52,615
Lots of action scenes when they do ramp into them.

176
00:08:53,275 --> 00:08:56,238
And then it's kind of subset by these

